" vim: set ft=vim:

""" Bash yourself to learn hjkl
    nnoremap <up> <nop>
    nnoremap <down> <nop>
    nnoremap <left> <nop>
    nnoremap <right> <nop>
    inoremap <up> <nop>
    inoremap <down> <nop>
    inoremap <left> <nop>
    inoremap <right> <nop>


""" Some tweaks for better life
    command! -bar -bang W :w<bang>
    command! -bar -bang Q :q<bang>
    command! -bar -bang Wc :wc<bang>
    command! -bar -bang Qc :qc<bang>
    command! -bar -bang Tabe :tabe<bang>


""" Stop help from not being helpful
    inoremap <F1> <ESC>
    nnoremap <F1> <ESC>
    vnoremap <F1> <ESC>


""" Little itch scratching
    nnoremap ; :


""" Make jj exit insert mode
    inoremap jj <ESC>


""" Move up and down rows and not lines when lines are wrapped
    nnoremap j gj
    nnoremap k gk


""" Open split window with ,w
    nnoremap <leader>w <C-w>v<C-w>l


""" Run things within vim with 'enter'
"    map <C-M> :make<CR>'


""" Make backspace behave
    set backspace=indent,eol,start


nnoremap <C-p> :FZF<CR>
